{"tid":832860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文盲台狗）誇張！台女歎杯珍珠奶茶　飲到一半驚見螺絲批","createTime":"2018-09-23T05:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T12:30:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e65c1671c160b1679c674c215ad88056631dcdde","tid":832860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180923/photo/bkn-20180923011256307-0923_00952_001_01p.jpg?20180923085905\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180923%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180923011256307-0923_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20180923085905&h=f8832d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲品藏「小強」、蒼蠅大家可能見得多，但成枝螺絲批大家又見過未？台灣一名女網民日前和朋友在高雄三民區，買了知名連鎖飲品店的珍珠奶茶，沒想到一行人正開心的享用飲品時，她竟發現杯子裏藏有一枝完整的螺絲批，讓她和朋友們都大呼不可思議。 <br />\n<br />\n女網民在Facebook群組發文，稱為了證明所言不假，歡迎店家翻查閉路電視畫面。至於為何這麼大的螺絲批，會喝到一半才發現，她解釋因為一開始杯子內的珍珠剛好擋住了，才會看不出來。 <br />\n<br />\n事件發生後，她致電店家告知此事，店家雖然表示要賠一杯，但她已再無喝飲料的慾望了。由於事件實在太罕見，貼文曝光後引來網民紛紛留言，「這也太誇張！整個螺絲起子（批）」；亦有網民笑言「原來是珍奶啊，還以為是雞尾酒」。"},{"pid":"497694b4a5d590e4a0620e9a94f81862dfad6e4a","tid":832860,"uid":204788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"加啲鐵質先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589d2947ad60c9b660cb5b86bfaaedd4717c6310","tid":832860,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"乜加螺絲批好飲d咩"},{"pid":"7d912d51196b9a7fb7e397421b15aaac19ccd742","tid":832860,"uid":153778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:44:13.000Z","msg":"依杯screwdriver黎，台狗識條鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310e130ed94aec1e6383f6aee5d1b5daa0665900","tid":832860,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"屌 我笑撚咗"},{"pid":"02eb7d9344b27064a84ac177180b4f8634405d46","tid":832860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2debbe23480efc20fe873b2af76638ae1e3130","tid":832860,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"賺咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7aa3ee4e15fd7ecea15456c69a7091ff5b6b5c6","tid":832860,"uid":86218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"神秘禮品黎<br />\n下之送螺絲錘仔畀你儲齊一套"},{"pid":"9af3822788899c4793c644b00b1d4564f95089df","tid":832860,"uid":194609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"落螺絲批咁dum本<br />\n想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f41f9366278fc7ed8c90b668f7e3cfaea7fe651","tid":832860,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cffa2828aec612c5ba6fc4a53a27a0ae4e08e6da","tid":832860,"uid":75521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"4387f326953c725969e00fa7de4259ef020ba3df","tid":832860,"uid":76753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:12:45.000Z","msg":"未食過kinder 出奇蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5612ea2269a20c2cd59a2137c1800a76dbced7","tid":832860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"台狗真係弱智㗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/853088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/853088</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}